{
  "texts": [
    "The search strategies are attached as Table 1, and search terms included LLM-related concepts such as \"large language models\" and \"GPT\", as well as healthcare-related concepts such as \"clinic\" or \"hospitals\".",
    "The reference section of previous reviews, as well as grey literature sources such as medRxiv, bioRxiv and arXiv, were hand searched for relevant publications.",
    "Eligibility criteriaWe included all publications that described the clinical applicability and usage of LLMs, including in inpatient, outpatient, and community settings.",
    "No restrictions were applied to the type of publications.",
    "Publications which did not focus on the use of LLM in clinical settings (e.g., assessed LLM applicability in medical education) were specifically excluded."
  ]
}